[buddycloud](http://buddycloud.org/) is group communication. Done Right.

Great social features, realtime updates, archives and message revocation.

Magically simple.

Using the buddycloud plugin you can receive updates on a buddycloud instance about GitHub events.

Install Notes
-------------

  1. buddycloud API base URL -- This is the base URL to the API for your buddycloud instance (no trailing slash)
  2. Username -- username for the posting account
  3. Password -- password for the posting account
  4. Channel -- the channel to which to post
  5. Choose whether to show a summary of commit messages, detailed commit information, or both